name: Delicate Chaos Rope Necklace
description:
"When I cannot tame the fires around me...I find peace in the delicate chaos inside me..." 

My favorite piece of the moment because I made these from nothing. The tangle pendant represents the "chaos" that surrounds us in our lives. Though often, it scares us, it's still so beautiful to us. 

Made with gold wire and strung on a gold filled chain at rope length (33")

name: Meditation Wrap Beads-Lucky
description:
Hand beaded with natural gemstones. Wear them to harness positive energy and attributes to positive living. Wear them as close to your body as possible. They can be worn as necklaces or wrapped around the wrists and fingers. Use them during prayers and/or meditation throughout your day. They are unisex and make great gifts for friends, family and co-workers. Available with 8mm or 10mm beads.

Made with natural green aventurine gemstone beads. Wear them to generate healing energy, bring good fortune and increase enthusiasm
